      "slide_or_page": 97,
      "element_type": "speaker_note",
      "element_id": "slide_97_notes",
      "source_text": "Tutor note: as this is the 1st assignment, tutor should make sure the session is as comprehensive as possible: As a minimum should cover:\nWriting the assignment webinar on LMS (30 mins) – this is on their LMS & guide students to view it\nAssignment guidance  and the assessment criteria document, which has been  highlighted to them at  induction by their programme lead\nEnsure students know about the importance of this document and that they can find them on their LMS.\nEnsure they know that this is a combined assignment\nShow the students the suggested structure in their assignment guidance document and link this through to the marking criteria\nBreak the question down into it’s relevant parts.\nEnsure they recognise the command words and how they guide the assignment\nRun a discussion with students on areas they are considering for product, service etc. & guide (not advise). Suggest they keep it simple\nGather student’s thoughts on relevant models/theories – final choice is the students\nEnd session by reminding students if they have any queries contact their programme lead as normal",
